reviewText: DONNIE MARTINEZ fights in this card, currently opening a gym out of Dallas TX he has talent that is not to be missed! If you want to see what a great fighter looks like then definitely get this DVD.

the first disk featured ryan darth bader and on one of the disks it featured a guy his nick name was little tito ortiz because he looks a lot like tito ortiz but he gets beat very early on by way of submission.
